CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 2, 1957, page 19, reads: "Special Guests... at the NAACP Human Rights dinner were, seated, left to right: Mrs. Robert L. Vann, Atty. Henry Smith, Irving Beauford, Matthew Moore, Mrs. Florence J. Reizenstein and Sylvester Anderson. Standing in the same order: Louis Mason Jr., Theodore Jones and Clarence (Larry) Huff. -'Teenie' Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Jessie Vann, Atty. Henry Smith, Irving Beauford, Matthew Moore, Florence J. Reizenstein, and Sylvester Anderson seated, with Louis Mason Jr., Theodore Jones, and Clarence "Larry" Huff standing behind them at NAACP Human Rights dinner
